#include<cstdio>
#include<iostream>
#include<cstring>
using namespace std;
struct Trie
{
    bool leaf;
    struct Trie *child[26];
    Trie()
    {
        leaf=false;
        for(int i=0;i<26;i++)
        child[i]=NULL;
    }
};
int main()
{
    int n;
    cin>>n;
    struct Trie *root;
    root=new Trie();
    root->leaf=false;
    while(n--)
    {
        string s;
        cin>>s;
        Trie *temp=root;
        int f=0;
        for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++)
        {
            if(temp->child[s[i]-'a']==NULL)
            {
                temp->child[s[i]-'a']=new Trie();
                f=1;
            }
            temp=temp->child[s[i]-'a'];
            if(temp->leaf and i!=s.length()-1)
            {
                cout<<"vulnerable\n";
                return 0;
            }
            if(i==s.length()-1)
            {
                temp->leaf=true;
                if(!f)
                {
                    cout<<"vulnerable\n";return 0;
                }

            }
        }
	
    }
    cout<<"non vulnerable\n";return 0;
}
